      Policy ‚Üê {ùïä requested:
        idx ‚Üê ‚äëcodes‚äê‚ü®<requested‚ü©
        result ‚Üê {state‚áê"error",currency‚áêrequested,max_fraction_digits‚áê¬Ø1,symbol‚áê"",code‚áê"unsupported_currency",message‚áê"unsupported currency: "‚àærequested}
        {ùïä:
          result ‚Ü© {state‚áê"ok",currency‚áê>idx‚äëcodes,max_fraction_digits‚áêidx‚äëmaxes,symbol‚áê>idx‚äësymbols,code‚áê"",message‚áê""}
        }‚çü(idx<‚âÝcodes) @
