      IsSupportedCurrency ‚Üê {ùïä requested: (Policy requested).state‚â°"ok"}
      result ‚Ü© {state‚áê"ok",code‚áê"",message‚áê"",registry‚áê{codes‚áê>¬®codes,Policy‚áêPolicy,IsSupportedCurrency‚áêIsSupportedCurrency}}
    }‚çü(fieldOk ‚àß codeOk ‚àß fractionOk ‚àß ¬¨duplicate) @
  }‚çü(0<‚âÝdata) @
